<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are some comments from the presidential
campaign trail:
   
   MICHAEL DUKAKIS, demanding to know why the Reagan administration
is doing business with Panamanian Gen. Manuel Antonio Noriega: ``I
and the American people want an explanation. ... Unless and until
we have that explanation, I'm not going to be satisfied.''
   
