happens to have the same name.''
   Jackson arrived in Los Angeles about 11 a.m. PDT Saturday to
address a crowd at the San Pedro yard, which has experienced
hundreds of layoffs in the past six years.
   Jackson was treated for back pain on New Year's Day at a
